Package org.treetank.node Description

Node Page Layer for Treetank

Here, all different nodes are listed which are used in Treetank. The nodes can be distinguished between AbsStructNode and AbsNode.

  • An AbsNode is the super type of all nodes. It implements the IItem Interface.
  • An AbsStructNode is the super type of all nodes. It inherits from the AbsNode .
